### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:3000/health

###

### 注册用户1（测试用，不发邮件）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "测试用户",
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "Test1234",
    "confirmPassword": "Test1234"
}

###

### 注册用户2（真实邮箱，测试邮件发送）
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "ChenSitian",
    "email": "180375278@qq.com",
    "password": "Csitian2026",
    "confirmPassword": "Csitian2026"
}

###

### 登录
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "Test1234"
}

###

### 检查邮箱
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/check-email?email=test@example.com

###

### 检查用户名
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/check-username?username=测试用户